{"tid":1332820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實「中共代理人」哩招可以點破","createTime":"2019-07-19T12:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:21:20.000Z","uid":40267,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3e970995fb41f4b8c13acf7ab83c1bc3583892cf","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"中共代理人<br />\n即係喺一啲國家選國家領導人哥陣<br />\n暗中資助並扶植一個親共人「中共代理人」去參選<br />\n如果選到既話可以令個國家直接投共or偏共<br />\n例子有台灣件發大財<br />\n當然扶植參選人之外仲要收買當地傳媒<br />\n台灣中天中視中時三個有中資背景既傳媒不斷咁幫發大財做勢<br />\n當然可以話年青人冇咁易上當<br />\n但大部分冇腦思想簡單既選民可能會上當<br />\n發大財就係咁做到市長<br />\n如果支共喺西方國家用哩招可以點防<br />\n你冇可能expect啲西方小國有英美哥種判斷力<br />\n<br />\n哩招其實好惡搞<br />\n有咩方法應對"},{"pid":"c472b470d2c8d8c1c37ad2aad9bc7ce9debe9234","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4137d743cf6a37828bfeb0aa1ff412e6b42d5b19","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"02a98f5bbcc803a645737e9acd6ca26023bf73e8","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7778acf0f9f7d02aff25c3844414f1813459324d","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f5d640bc186571d274a909a50c1291aaae19e88e","tid":1332820,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"咪做緊"},{"pid":"103c3ba027eb04c899240518336cb2b7a250eaa0","tid":1332820,"uid":3571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6091b53735994f4b3245a5f4cab642bee1058801","tid":1332820,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"103c3ba027eb04c899240518336cb2b7a250eaa0","tid":1332820,"uid":3571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:58:40.000Z","msg":